a.xlink:title:
aind_data_schema.core.acquisition.Acquisition
Description of an imaging acquisition session
Attributes: protocol_id (List[str]): DOI for protocols.io. Default is []. experimenter_full_name (List[str]): First and last name of the experimenter(s). calibrations (List[Calibration]): List of calibration measurements taken prior to acquisition. Default is []. maintenance (List[Maintenance]): List of maintenance on rig prior to acquisition. Default is []. processing_steps (List[ProcessingSteps]): List of downstream processing steps planned for each channel. Default is [].

aind_data_schema.models.coordinates.ImageAxis
Description of an image axis
Attributes: direction (AnatomicalDirection(str, Enum)): Tissue direction as the value of axis increases. If Other describe in notes. dimension (int): Reference axis number for stitching

aind_data_schema.models.devices.Calibration
Generic calibration class
Attributes: device_name (str): Must match a device name in rig/instrument description (str): Brief description of what is being calibrated input (AindGenericType): Calibration input. Default is . output (AindGenericType): Calibration output. Default is .

aind_data_schema.models.devices.Maintenance
Generic maintenance class
Attributes: device_name (str): Must match a device name in rig/instrument description (str): Description on maintenance procedure

aind_data_schema.imaging.tile.Channel
Description of a channel
Attributes: light_source_name (str): Must match device name filter_names (List[str]): Must match device names detector_name (str): Must match device name

aind_data_schema.models.coordinates.Affine3dTransform
Values to be vector-added to a 3D position. Often needed to specify a Tile's origin.

aind_data_schema.models.coordinates.Rotation3dTransform
Values to be vector-added to a 3D position. Often needed to specify a device or tile's origin.

aind_data_schema.models.coordinates.Scale3dTransform
Values to be vector-multiplied with a 3D position, equivalent to the diagonals of a 3x3 transform matrix. Represents voxel spacing if used as the first applied coordinate transform.

aind_data_schema.models.coordinates.Translation3dTransform
Values to be vector-added to a 3D position. Often needed to specify a device or tile's origin.

aind_data_schema.models.reagent.Reagent
Description of reagent used in procedure
